name: Opuntia Pixelenius
description:
This year was very difficult for us)

But let's take care of our little coniferous brothers. This is just another day and the fact that it means something to us does not mean that the trees should suffer from this. Don't waste your finances on bouquets for girls. These dead flowers are just another absurd business, and they don't last a couple of days at best. Another thing is the cactus. Its fractal geometry is much older evolutionarily, not only of all these stupid superstitious holidays, but of the entire human race as a whole. The emergence of these beautiful creations is shrouded in mystery. Most cactus do not require intensive grooming and NFT cactus even more so. Now it's yours) Good luck!
